{
  "stem": "7069.5",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And as I get closer and closer, there's one guy in front of me yet.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he takes the slip from this guy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And while he takes the slip away from this guy, another SS man comes from somewhere and taps this guard on the shoulder.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he and his helper both turn-- turn around to face this guard that tapped him on the shoulder.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I just snuck in at that moment.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean, you can't plan it that way.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's a miracle that happens.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So now there I am, inside.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My problems aren't over yet.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I'm inside and I'm being-- there's one guy that looks at what-- what the reason is for your being there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he sees that swelling.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he sends me to a line.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I'm-- in front of me there are maybe five or six other prisoners with similar things.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They have these swellings on the-- on the-- on our chest, on our legs, all over the place, similar things like that.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there I see this-- this doctor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "An SS man in-- in a general's rank.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Schmitz ?] was his name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I can never forget it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He takes care of these people, quote, unquote, 'takes care.' He stands there in his white smock, and has two huge helpers that take these-- the guy that comes in, take those guys like, in a-- in a vise, by their arms.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And this doctor just takes the scalpel and just cuts them open, slits them open.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Takes a paper towel, wipes it off, puts it down, until next guy comes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Now, I noticed-- of course, naturally these guys were hollering and yelling.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the moment they were hollering he took the fist and hit them.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
